%% NOON Dashboard 性能优化 — 时序图
%% 文件: docs/sequence-diagram.mermaid
%% 包含三条关键链路：翻页/筛选/排序、发起抓取→轮询→刷新、总览页加载

%% ===== 链路 1：翻页/筛选/排序 =====
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant DBPage as DatabasePage
    participant GF as useGlobalFilters
    participant UP as useProducts(params)
    participant API as FastAPI /products/
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>DBPage: 点击排序/翻页/选类目
    DBPage->>GF: setSortConfig/setPagination/setSelectedCategory
    Note over GF: 状态变更触发 re-render

    GF->>UP: params={page,pageSize,category,q,sort,order}
    Note over UP: queryKey变化自动refetch<br/>placeholderData=keepPreviousData

    UP->>API: GET /products/?skip=0&limit=20&category=按摩器&sort=price&order=desc
    API->>API: build_category_filter("按摩器")→OR复合SQL
    API->>API: _latest_snapshot_subquery()→窗口函数取最新快照
    API->>DB: SELECT tp.*, ps.price... JOIN latest_snapshot<br/>WHERE... ORDER BY ps.price DESC LIMIT 20 OFFSET 0
    DB-->>API: 20行商品+快照字段

    API->>DB: SELECT count(*) WHERE...(同过滤条件)
    DB-->>API: total=320

    API-->>UP: {items: Product[20], total: 320}
    UP-->>DBPage: data.items渲染表格, data.total渲染分页器
    Note over DBPage: 受控模式:不调用<br/>getPaginationRowModel/getSortedRowModel

%% ===== 链路 2：发起抓取→轮询→刷新 =====
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant App as App.tsx
    participant SC as useScrapeController
    participant QC as QueryClient
    participant API as FastAPI /tasks/

    User->>App: 提交搜索表单
    App->>SC: triggerScrape(query, pages, provider)
    SC->>SC: setScraping(true), setWaitingForLog(true)
    SC->>API: POST /tasks/search {task_type, query, ...}
    API-->>SC: {job_id}

    SC->>SC: handleExecutionUpdate(jobId,...)创建ExecutionBlock
    SC->>SC: pollTaskUntilDone(jobId) setInterval 2s

    SC->>QC: invalidateQueries(['tasks'])
    SC->>QC: invalidateQueries(['products'])
    SC->>QC: invalidateQueries(['stats'])

    loop 每2s直到SUCCESS/FAILED
        SC->>QC: refetchQueries(['tasks'])
        QC->>API: GET /tasks/?limit=20
        API-->>QC: Task[]
        QC-->>SC: tasks更新
        SC->>SC: useEffect(tasks变化)同步executionBlocks
        alt 任务终态
            SC->>SC: clearInterval
            SC->>QC: invalidateQueries(['products'])
            SC->>QC: invalidateQueries(['stats'])
            Note over QC: 触发useProducts+useProductDistribution重新拉取
        end
    end

    SC-->>App: {scraping, waitingForLog, executionBlocks}
    App-->>User: 系统日志显示执行块,大盘数据刷新

%% ===== 链路 3：总览页加载（改造后） =====
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as App(lazy import)
    participant OVP as OverviewPage
    participant UPD as useProductDistribution
    participant UC as useCategories
    participant API as FastAPI

    App->>OVP: Suspense > OverviewPage
    Note over OVP: 不再接收products/filteredProducts props

    OVP->>UPD: useProductDistribution(selectedCategory)
    OVP->>UC: useCategories()

    par 并行请求
        UPD->>API: GET /products/stats?category=All
        API->>API: 聚合全量ACTIVE商品
        API-->>UPD: DistributionStats
    and
        UC->>API: GET /products/categories
        API-->>UC: [{label,count},...]
    end

    OVP->>OVP: 直接渲染聚合数据(删除4个useMemo)
    Note over OVP: stats卡片←DistributionStats<br/>类目tab←useCategories<br/>价格分布图←price_distribution<br/>散点图←scatter_data<br/>品牌TOP10←brand_ranking
